sql:
SELECT location
FROM charging_stations
WHERE availability = (SELECT MAX(availability) FROM charging_stations);

SELECT status
FROM electric_vehicles
WHERE status = 'operational';

SELECT location
FROM charging_stations
WHERE next_maintenance_date = (SELECT MIN(next_maintenance_date) FROM charging_stations);

external_knowledge:
- A vehicle is considered to have had recent maintenance if its last maintenance date is within the last 6 months; 
- The time frame of "the last month" refers to the period from the current date to one month ago; 
- The "top 5" vehicles are determined by the highest total energy consumption.

